        <item>
            <title>【CES 2024】LG Signature OLED T 電視	透明屏幕搶眼 + 極強科幻感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:17:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lg]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Signature OLED T]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1213776</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>除了宣佈與 Google 合作的新聞外，LG 發佈會最矚目的肯定是全無線設計兼擁有透明熒幕的 LG Signature OLED T 電視首度真身亮相。Edward 就在發佈會為大家近距離拍到它的外貌，現在就與大家分享一下這款既富藝術感亦有極強科幻感的全新旗艦電視吧。</p><h2>全透明熒幕不破壞家居設計</h2><p>LG 最新推出的 Signature OLED T，最特別之處肯定是它的 77 吋全透明設計的 4K OLED 面板。傳統智能電視始終有硬件、背板等，所以掛在客廳牆上，始終會破壞整體家居設計氛圍。而 LG 今次推出的 Signature OLED T，就採用全透明熒幕設計，配以極幼的熒幕邊框，令它即使放在窗前，用家也可以穿透電視熒幕看到背後的窗外風景，同時間採用透明玻璃的電視熒幕仍會顯示內容，在藝術感上它不會破壞整體家居設計氛圍（當然它始終仍有邊框及仍可頗明顯看到熒幕玻璃，未做到完全隱形，但已比傳統電視好得多），而透明玻璃同時為用家帶來資訊及電視後的風景也讓用家猶如置身科幻感極強的空間內，筆者現場肉眼所見，觀感確實十分震撼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LG 發佈會的重磅消息，肯定是這部全新無線電視 Signature OLED T 的發佈啦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003326.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003334.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲它最特別之處肯定是 77 吋的全透明 4K OLED 熒幕，筆者現場所見真的可以透過面板清晰看到電視背後的景物，十分厲害。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005422.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上電視透框依然十分幼，所以它的「隱形度」相比傳統電視確實高很多。不過 LG 方面表示這設計仍非最終定案，外框仍然在開發中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003358.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而且不只是電視熒幕關上時，即使啟動後在顯示內容，仍可透過透明熒幕看到背後風景，藝術感及科幻感均十分強。</p><h2>睇片時可將熒幕變非透明</h2><p>可能大家會問：如此「通透」，萬一瀏覽影片時豈非對畫面有所影響？LG 亦有想到這一點，用家只需要在睇片時將透明模式關閉，就可令熒幕變成非透明，就不會對欣賞影片有所影響了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003434.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_003443.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當然，透明熒幕在播放影片時始終對畫質有一定影響，尤其是背後風景如果是較光亮。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005333.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲所以它的「透明模式」是可以關閉的，關上後瀏覽觀感就與一般 4K OLED 電視分別不大。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005418.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而顯示相比影片較靜態的畫面時，透明模式確實可為用家帶來十分震撼的視覺效果。</p><h2>仍採全無線設計 + 極幼邊框</h2><p>至於電視設計上，大致上與去年 CES 大展現身過的 M 系無線電視差不多，主機板及各種接駁端子仍然保留在另設的「小盒子」上，畫面就會透過無線方式傳輸到電視上播放。官方亦有表示這次看到的外型不一定是最終成品，它的外殼仍然在開發中，而推出日期及售價亦未定，不過應該最快也要年底，也應該是「天價」品吧。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_20240109_005410.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Signature OLED T 仍然採用類似 M 系無線電視的設計，所以主機板、端子等仍然設於這個「小盒子」內，並以無線模式傳輸影像到電視播放。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/steam-deck-oled-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Steam Deck OLED 電腦遊戲掌機，熒幕超亮麗 + 續航、遊戲效能有驚喜</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/steam-deck-hk/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Steam Deck OLED 2023 香港開箱評測，效能，熒幕，續航力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/lg-announce-coop-with-google/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 宣佈與 Google 合作	2024 起 OLED TV 將預載支援 Chromecast 及 Google Home</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/ces2024-lg-signature-oled-t-close-up/wireless-home/audio-visual/">【CES 2024】LG Signature OLED T 電視	透明屏幕搶眼 + 極強科幻感</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
