            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA GeForce RTX 40 SUPER 系列正式在 CES 2024 消費電子產品展覽發佈。全新產品線包括有 GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER、GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 和 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER。SUPER 系列帶來了效能提升，除了為遊戲帶來更流暢體驗之外，也為 AI 應用提供更強的處理能力。公版 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 今日就新鮮熱辣來到了 unwire 編輯部，就等小編同大家先開箱看看這張新卡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08772.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08775.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08748.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08744.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08776.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07973.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 RTX 4070 SUPER 同樣使用到最新電源轉換線供電，需要連接兩條 PCI-e 電源線</p><p>我們將在日後提供更詳細評測、跑分測試結果給大家參考。今次就先同大家開箱。從相片中可看到，GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 公版卡卡身用上黑色金屬外殼，外殼大小與早前推出的 RTX 4070、RTX 4060Ti 沒有看得出的分別。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08762.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以公版卡來説 RTX 4070（上）、RTX 4070 SUPER（下） 體積大致相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08766.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ RTX 4070（後方）、RTX 4070 SUPER（前方） 體積大致相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08757.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三張顯示卡厚度比對</p><p>而同 RTX 4090、RTX 4080 比較，本卡的體積明顯更為細小，更適合細機箱用戶選購。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213644" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08760-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲將歷代公版卡作一個比較 (4060 Ti 乃非公版)，可看到體積、長度大致分為兩種，而今次的 RTX 4070 SUPER 卡身就幾乎同 RTX 4070, RTX 4060 Ti 相同</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08761.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲單純比較 RTX 4090（上）與 RTX 4070 SUPER（下）的卡面面積分別</p><p>NVIDIA 一次過為 RTX 4080、RTX 4070 Ti 同 RTX 4070 都作一個全面升級。這三款顯示卡可説是中階、中高階入門之選，在非 SUPER 版推出時因為各種因素，包括售價、供應，未能完全令遊戲用家受落。今次推出 SUPER 版本，三個型號都有效能提升。重點是 SUPER 版效能提升，但價錢保持不變，今次開箱的 GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 的售價為 US$599（約港幣 HK$4,677），美金價與當初 RTX 4070 推出時相同。</p><p>最新三款 RTX 40 SUPER 系列售價：</p><p>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER US$999 起（約港幣 HK$7,799）</p><p>1 月 31 日起發售</p><p>GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER US$799 起（約港幣 HK$6,238）</p><p>1 月 24 日起發售</p><p>GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER US$599 起（約港幣 HK$4,677）</p><p>1 月 17 日起發售</p><p>再睇睇 RTX 4070 SUPER 卡身更多細節：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08743.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08753.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08755-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08756.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲公版卡提供 1 個 HDMI 插口與 3 個 DisplayPort 插口</p><p>今次 NVIDIA 為最新的 SUPER 系列分割了 3 個不同的客戶羣。用戶可按需要購入適合自己的顯示卡。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER：4G 遊戲怪獸</h2><p>NVIDIA 形容 GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER 非常適合在 4K 解像度流暢地享受遊戲。本卡內置基於 NVIDIA Ada Lovelace 架構的圖像處理器，提供最高 52 Shader-TFLOP/s、121 RT TLOPS 以及 836 AI TOPS 的性能。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER：中階用家頂尖之選</h2><p>用於想選購中階卡的用戶來説，GeForce RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 可以在 1440p 畫質下提供極高流暢度，也支援 4K 的遊戲體驗。相對於 RTX 4070 Ti，它內置有更多 CUDA 核心，擴增到 16GB 的幀緩衝區和 256 位元的記憶體匯流排，記憶體頻寬提升至 672GB/s。它的效能比起 RTX 3070 Ti 快 1.6 倍，在 DLSS 3 的加成下更可達 2.5 倍。</p><h2>GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER：更好的平衡</h2><p>今次 RTX 4070 SUPER 比起 RTX 4070 多出 20% 核心，相信將會是極高性價比的新產品（請留意我們不久後推出的評測文章）。NVIDIA 指它比起 RTX 3090 更快、功耗更低；在 DLSS 3 的加成下，更是有 1.5 倍的效能。顯示卡同樣支援深度學習超級採樣 DLSS，以 AI 人工智能驅動，在遊戲中生成畫格與重建光線，結合光線追蹤，提供更流暢的遊戲體驗。</p><p>詳細測試報告及規格，會在日後再為大家送上。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc08746.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1213661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc07971-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER 和 4070 SUPER，NVIDIA 創始版設計將直接通過 NVIDIA.com 和選定零售商提供。包括原廠時脈和超頻版在內的自訂板卡，適用於所有 GeForce RTX 40 SUPER 系列 GPU，將由供應商如 ASUS、Colorful、Gainward、GALAX、GIGABYTE、INNO3D、KFA2、MSI、Palit、PNY 和 ZOTAC 提供。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/lg-announce-coop-with-google/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 宣佈與 Google 合作	2024 起 OLED TV 將預載支援 Chromecast 及 Google Home</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/08/ces-2024-lg-projector-and-gaming-monitor/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】LG 細小投影機 + 電競螢幕   4K UHD 鐳射投影 + 240Hz 0.03 ms 曲面 OLED</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/08/ces-2024-evie-ring/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】EVIE 智能戒指，追蹤身體數據 + 記錄月經</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/">【開箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 顯示卡　搶先看 Founder Edition 真身</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
